' Pumpkin Spice example 5
' ASK block

' Sometimes you want to ask a Yes/No question

COLOR 2
SAY "Greeting Profressor Falken."

ASK "Would you like to play Global Thermonuclear War?"
' Specify colors here
ASK COLOR 2
ASK BGCOLOR 0
ASK PROMPT COLOR 2
' You may specify a default response to the question with
' DEFAULT YES
'  or
' DEFAULT NO
ON YES
  ' This runs when the users picks Yes
  SAY "A strange game."
  SLEEP 400
  SAY "The only winning move is not to play."
  SLEEP 400
  SAY "You lose"
ON NO
  ' This runs when the users picks No
  SAY "You're no fun."
END ASK